{"about_the_game":"Step into the shoes of Indigo, the owner of a quaint spell shop in a city with no magic. Help your customers with a wide variety of problems!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Spellwriting</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473030/extras/SpellWriting.gif?t=1719507786\" /><br>Craft spells as unique as your customers! Wield the power of 24 distinct magical glyphs which can be combined into precise spells. Use your problem solving and creativity to fit the best spells to each customer!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Phone</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473030/extras/Phone.gif?t=1719507786\" /><br>In a modern world, of course Indigo has a phone! Get text messages, write notes, play games, and more on your phone when you should be working instead! Phones are a great form of distraction and entertainment, and what you find may be affected by the spells you give out!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Workshop</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2473030/extras/CharacterEditor.gif?t=1719507786\" /><br>There is a character creator available in game to make your own characters! Set the images, dialogue, and more to make a character! Then, easily upload your character to the workshop and download others to play with them in custom days! <br><br><br>Unlock the potential of magic and savor the delightfully heartwarming outcomes of all the spells you bestow upon those who come, with results that can be astonishingly positive! (or perhaps... entertainingly unpredictable. But hey, what's magic without a little mystery and mischief, right?)","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I know what I'm doing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2473030/0d3ad1b23c0e199f648faffa08b7a6ef5a205f58.jpg"},{"name":"Here you go","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunit